# Terrorists to Communists

The Red Scare returns, coming soon to a browser near you. McCarthyism, the browser extension.


## Installation

[Download for Chrome](https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/terrorists-to-communists/pddpoicomcfeklpandjbocolimheohcn?hl=en-US&gl=US&authuser=1)

[Download for Firefox](https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/terrorists-to-communists/)

